markets.question: Will Bitcoin exceed $150,000 by July 2026?
markets.description: This market will resolve to 'Yes' if the price of Bitcoin (BTC) exceeds $150,000 USD at any point before July 1, 2026.

markets.question: Will the Fed cut rates in Q1 2026?
markets.description: Resolves 'Yes' if the Federal Reserve announces a rate cut during Q1 2026.

markets.question: Will Tesla stock close above $500 by March 2026?
markets.description: Resolves 'Yes' if TSLA closes above $500 on any trading day before March 31, 2026.

markets.question: Super Bowl LX: Will the Chiefs win?
markets.description: Resolves 'Yes' if the Kansas City Chiefs win Super Bowl LX.

markets.question: Will GPT-5 be released before July 2026?
markets.description: Resolves 'Yes' if OpenAI publicly releases GPT-5 before July 1, 2026.

markets.question: Will there be a US government shutdown in 2026?
markets.description: Resolves 'Yes' if the US federal government experiences a shutdown of any duration in 2026.

markets.question: Will Ethereum flip Bitcoin in market cap by 2027?
markets.description: Resolves 'Yes' if Ethereum's market cap exceeds Bitcoin's at any point before January 1, 2027.

markets.question: Academy Awards 2026: Will an AI-generated film win Best Picture?
markets.description: Resolves 'Yes' if a film with significant AI-generated content wins Best Picture at the 2026 Academy Awards.

markets.question: Will Apple release AR glasses in 2026?
markets.description: Resolves 'Yes' if Apple releases consumer AR glasses (not Vision Pro) in 2026.

markets.question: NBA Finals 2026: Will the Celtics repeat?
markets.description: Resolves 'Yes' if the Boston Celtics win the 2026 NBA Finals.
